# 🚀 Awwwards-Level 3D Portfolio — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A complete architectural rebuild of the existing React/Vite portfolio into a premium, immersive, interactive portfolio with Three.js 3D scenes, Framer Motion animations, Lenis smooth scroll, and a custom cursor.

---

## Packages Installed

```bash
@react-three/fiber @react-three/drei three
framer-motion
gsap @gsap/react
lenis
tailwindcss@3 postcss autoprefixer
```

