## Running Locally

```bash
npm run dev      # http://localhost:5173
npm run build    # Production bundle
```

## Deploy to Vercel

1. Push to GitHub
2. Go to [vercel.com](https://vercel.com) → Import project
3. Select the repo → Framework: **Vite** → Deploy ✓

## Deploy to Netlify

```bash
npm run build
# Upload the dist/ folder at app.netlify.com/drop
```
